 ricane Preparedness Expo - your one-stop event to get storm-ready before h
 urricane season starts June 1st . Join us on May 30\, 2026\, from 11:00 AM
  to 3:00 PM at Cordelia B Hunt Center located at 4810 N Himes Ave Tampa\, 
 Florida 33614 Come out and: Stock up on essential hurricane preparedness s
 upplies Pick up sandbags to help protect your home.( Limit 10 bags per fam
 ily while supplies last ) Learn how to keep your family safe this season D
